we ourselves either

01:09:54.090 --> 01:09:57.690
uphold those inequalities,
perpetuate those inequalities,

01:09:57.690 --> 01:10:00.460
or benefit from those
inequalities, right?

01:10:00.460 --> 01:10:02.100
And so we have to,
I think that if we

01:10:02.100 --> 01:10:05.130
talk about things in the
language of exclusion,

01:10:05.130 --> 01:10:08.100
there's almost a responsibility
and accountability

01:10:08.100 --> 01:10:12.396
to the effects that
those exclusions have.

